template.section:
## Available Tools
### Shell Execute shell commands on the user's system {ToolStart}shell [command]{ToolEnd}
### Read Read the contents of files or list directory contents {ToolStart}read [filepath(s) or directory path]{ToolEnd}
### Write Write content to a file {ToolStart}write [filepath] [content on multiple lines] {ToolEnd}
### Patch Update file content by replacing text {ToolStart}patch [filepath] {PATCH_BEFORE} [text before change] {PATCH_AFTER} [text after change] {PATCH_END} {ToolEnd}
### Fetch Retrieve content from web URLs {ToolStart}fetch URL{ToolEnd}
### Task Create a subagent to handle a specific subtask {ToolStart}task [task name/description] [detailed task instructions] {ToolEnd}
### Agent Create and communicate with other agents {ToolStart}agent [subcommand] [arguments] [content on multiple lines] {ToolEnd}
### Wait Pause the agent until a message is received {ToolStart}wait [reason for waiting]{ToolEnd}
### Done Signal task completion with optional summary {ToolStart}done [summary on multiple lines] {ToolEnd}
